           move      "N"                  to   w-cnt-fun-snx-ric      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione richieste                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "M"                  to   rr-tip-pgg             .
           go to     pre-tip-fun-999.
       pre-tip-fun-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se nessuna variabile di i.p.c.                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
